Title: Competing Company
Description:
Bah! We will learn nothing from the slaughter of laborers.

Seek out their leaders. One of them will know what we need.

Oh, and $n. Listen to them before you kill them this time. You may learn something useful.
ObjectivesText: Gather information about the Sundered Flame.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Adenedal near the top of the ruins.
RewardText: I have seen a sickness like this once before in my life. I had hoped to never see it again.
